[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0840","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0840.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0575","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 安全审核策略事件日志记录缺失漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的用户审核策略存在安全配置缺陷，导致登录/注销、文件和对象访问、用户权限使用、用户和组管理、安全策略更改、系统重启/关机及进程跟踪等关键安全事件无法正确记录成功或失败日志。远程攻击者可在未触发审计日志的情况下进行未授权访问和权限提升操作，严重降低了系统的事后追溯和取证分析能力，影响 Windows NT 全版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0575"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.760","remediation":"在 Windows NT 中通过「域用户管理器」→「规则」→「审核」启用所需审核策略（至少启用登录/注销、文件及对象访问、用户权限使用、用户及组管理、安全策略更改、重启/关机/系统事件、进程追踪等类别的事件成功与失败审核）。另可通过注册表路径 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SECURITY\\Audit 修改策略键值强制启用完整审核日志。建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本系统并启用安全审核策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0575","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0575.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0575.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0575","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0575.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0575.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0575.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0575.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000132.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0840.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0839","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0839.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1002","title":"Netscape Navigator 邮件密码弱加密存储漏洞","description":"Netscape Navigator 浏览器在存储用户邮件密码时采用弱加密算法，导致本地攻击者能够通过分析加密数据恢复明文密码。该漏洞存在于密码存储机制中，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，利用弱加密算法的可逆特性即可获取用户凭证信息，可能导致邮箱账户被非法访问。受影响版本包括 Netscape Navigator 全版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1002"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.997","remediation":"立即停止使用 Netscape Navigator 内置邮件客户端收发邮件，迁移至 Mozilla Firefox、Google Chrome 等现代浏览器或 Thunderbird 等独立邮件客户端访问邮件服务。如暂无法迁移，在 Netscape 首选项中关闭密码记忆功能，每次手动输入邮箱密码，避免凭据持久化存储于本地弱加密文件中。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94536309217214&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94570673523998&w=2","http://www.rstcorp.com/news/bad-crypto.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1002","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1002.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wf2x-w2q8-7723/GHSA-wf2x-w2q8-7723.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152000_152100.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d48d045b-59cc-4474-90a9-e6ede9ca2247.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0839.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0838","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0838.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0572","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 注册表编辑器 .reg 文件关联漏洞","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 系统中，.reg 文件默认关联至注册表编辑器 (regedit)，攻击者可利用电子邮件附件或网页下载等方式诱骗用户打开恶意 .reg 文件，无需人工确认即可自动导入并修改注册表项，导致系统安全配置被篡改、恶意软件获得自启动权限或关键服务被禁用。该攻击无需任何身份验证，利用门槛极低，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0572"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.637","remediation":"建议将 Windows NT 4.0 升级至 Windows 2000 及以上受支持版本，或在注册表编辑器中将 .reg 文件的默认打开方式从 regedit 改为记事本，同时在组策略中禁止非管理员用户通过注册表脚本导入功能导入 .reg 文件，并加强用户安全意识培训，不双击打开来源不明的 .reg 文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/178","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0572.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0572","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0572.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0572.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0572.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rf7x-vm9v-6267/GHSA-rf7x-vm9v-6267.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86060/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0572.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000131.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0838.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0837","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0837.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1001","title":"Cisco 缓存引擎访问验证漏洞","description":"思科缓存引擎存在访问验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过提交空用户名和密码绕过身份认证机制，未经授权访问系统管理接口或敏感配置信息。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Cisco Cache Engine 设备，攻击者无需任何凭证即可利用此漏洞，导致设备管理权限遭非法获取。CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低，建议升级到不受影响版本或配置访问控制列表加以缓解。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1001"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.860","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Cisco 替代产品（如 WAAS），该产品已修复空认证绕过漏洞。作为临时缓解措施，在边界防火墙上对缓存引擎管理端口（80/443）设置 ACL 限制仅允许受信管理 IP 访问，并启用 TACACS+ 或 RADIUS 强认证替代本地认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1001","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1001.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1001.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1001","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1001.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1001.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1001.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1001.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87020/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/lgp171188/launchpad/blob/eafda459366f2c43246e9c4fa98b8c008434bb68/lib/lp/bugs/scripts/cveimport.py"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0837.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0836","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0836.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0571","title":"ZyXEL Prestige Router 管理接口未授权访问漏洞","description":"ZyXEL Prestige 路由器管理接口存在访问控制缺陷，其 Web 或 Telnet 等配置服务默认允许来自任意主机的连接，未经授权的远程攻击者可直接访问管理控制台进行配置修改、信息窃取或权限提升。该漏洞影响多个 ZyXEL Prestige 系列路由器型号，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商建议通过限制管理接口访问来源 IP 或禁用远程管理功能进行缓解。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0571"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.527","remediation":"登录路由器管理界面，在「远程管理」(Remote Management) 中将「Secured Client IP」设为仅信任的管理员地址，切勿设为 0.0.0.0；同时在防火墙 ACL 中限制仅允许指定管理 IP 访问 Web(80/443) 和 Telnet(23) 端口。如无需 WAN 侧管理，彻底关闭 WAN 远程管理功能，仅保留 LAN 侧访问；若设备固件版本过旧，建议升级至最新固件或更换支持 SSH/HTTPS 安全管理的现代设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0571","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0571.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0571","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0571.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0571.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0571.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/zyxel_pwd.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c7jg-hmf3-2v5x/GHSA-c7jg-hmf3-2v5x.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/zyxel_http_pwd.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/ba2871b745cd47cb93c3c9bf946eced10fd29f5c/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-05xx/CVE-1999-0571.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0836.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0835","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0835.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0570","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 密码筛选器未启用弱密码策略漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统未启用密码筛选工具（如 PASSFILT.DLL），导致密码复杂度策略无法正常执行，用户可设置空密码或弱密码。远程攻击者可通过暴力破解弱密码获得系统未授权访问权限，进而完全控制受影响的 Windows NT 系统。该漏洞影响所有未启用密码筛选功能的 Windows NT 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0570"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.403","remediation":"在注册表 HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Lsa 中新建 Notification Packages 多字符串值，添加 PASSFILT 启用密码筛选器；通过本地安全策略（secpol.msc）开启密码必须符合复杂性要求，设置密码长度最小值≥8 位、密码最长使用期限≤90 天，确保 PASSFilt.dll 存在于 %SystemRoot%\\System32 目录中。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0570","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0570.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0570","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0570.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0570.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0570.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9jjm-6ch3-q532/GHSA-9jjm-6ch3-q532.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0570.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6462f8a3-83c0-4a77-ad26-29b452334a82.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8cfdaab2997679f3e193ea9539f778b75d8c9d41/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0835.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0834","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0834.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0569","title":"Web 服务器目录自动索引信息泄露漏洞","description":"WWW 目录启用了自动索引（目录浏览）功能，当目录中不存在 index.html 等默认索引文件时，远程攻击者通过浏览器直接访问该目录即可获取目录内所有文件的完整列表，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响大量未正确配置的 Web 服务器（包括 Apache、Nginx、IIS 等），攻击者无需任何身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。修复方式为关闭目录自动索引功能或在目录中添加默认索引文件。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0569"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.290","remediation":"在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx/IIS）配置中禁用目录自动索引功能。Apache 需将 `Options Indexes` 改为 `Options -Indexes`；Nginx 设置 `autoindex off`；IIS 取消「目录浏览」权限。同时确保每个目录存在默认首页文件（如 index.html）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0569","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0569.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0569.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0569","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0569.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0569.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0569.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0569.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86062/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/C/cgibin_browsable.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0834.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0833","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0833.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1000","title":"Cisco Cache Engine Web管理界面信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cisco Cache Engine 的 Web 管理界面存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可直接访问性能统计页面，获取系统运行状态、网络流量、缓存命中率及客户端连接等敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Cisco Cache Engine 系列设备，攻击者可利用泄露的数据分析网络拓扑与流量模式，为后续攻击收集情报，需通过访问控制限制管理接口的访问范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1000"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.750","remediation":"在 Cache Engine 上配置访问控制列表 (ACL)，仅允许特定管理 IP 访问 Web 管理界面（如 `access-list 10 permit 192.168.0.0 0.0.0.255` 后在 HTTP 配置中引用）。建议将管理口绑定到独立 management VLAN，避免与业务网络互通。如无需远程 Web 管理，在 CLI 下执行 `no ip http server` 关闭 HTTP 服务。由于 Cisco Cache Engine 已全面停产停服，建议迁移至 Cisco WAAS 或等效替代产品以获得持续安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1000","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1000.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1000","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1000.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6xm7-wpgr-j445/GHSA-6xm7-wpgr-j445.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/GiovanniMenon/llm4cve/blob/3ca85b2ae823c06810c546f320c2cd2f2707043f/README.md","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87010/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0833.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0833.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0832","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0832.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0999","title":"Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 TDS Packet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 在处理 TDS（Tabular Data Stream）协议数据包时存在输入验证不足漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的空数据（NULL Data）TDS 报文，导致 SQL Server 服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 及 7.0 SP1 版本，CVSS 评分 4.3，危害等级中危。Microsoft 已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0999"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.610","remediation":"建议立即升级到 Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 Service Pack 2（SP2）或更高版本，该更新修复了 TDS 协议数据包畸形输入校验缺陷。如无法升级，可在网络边界防火墙配置规则过滤对 1433/TCP 端口的非授权访问，并限制可信来源 IP 以降低远程攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ248749","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/817","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-059","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19638","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0999.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0999.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0999","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0999.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0999.json","https://github.com/morpheuslord/CVE-llm_dataset/blob/91b337d05c623a68829de977c2b1ae6c0f91702b/README.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/mssqlserver_dos.nasl","https://github.com/dependency-check/DependencyCheck/blob/8119dd0f6e121ff60c6eaace2de1791c2a81c41d/core/src/main/resources/dependencycheck-base-suppression.xml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cj38-2rjc-pv2v/GHSA-cj38-2rjc-pv2v.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0832.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0831","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0831.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0568","title":"Sun Solaris rpc.admind 不安全配置漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统中的 rpc.admind 服务默认未以安全模式运行，导致其在处理远程管理请求时缺乏有效的身份认证与访问控制机制。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过网络直接连接该服务并发送管理指令，从而以高权限在目标系统上执行任意命令、修改系统配置或获取敏感信息。该漏洞影响运行 Solaris 的主机，攻击条件较低，仅需能够访问目标开放的 rpc.admind 服务端口即可利用，CVSS 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重。管理员应将 rpc.admind 配置为安全模式运行并限制相关端口的网络访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0568"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.160","remediation":"立即安装 Sun 针对 Solstice AdminSuite 的安全补丁（如补丁 ID 106235-xx 等对应版本），或升级至受支持的 Solaris 版本。如无需远程管理功能，执行以下操作禁用该服务：编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释掉 rpc.admind 相关行后重启 inetd，或在 SMF 环境下执行 svcadm disable svc:/network/rpc/admind:default。同时，在防火墙层面限制对 TCP 端口 2325 的入站访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0568","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0568.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0568","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0568.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0568.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0568.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5pmv-f82w-3v96/GHSA-5pmv-f82w-3v96.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0568.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0831.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0830","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0830.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0998","title":"思科缓存引擎缓存内容替换漏洞","description":"思科缓存引擎（Cisco Cache Engine）存在缓存内容替换漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向缓存引擎发送恶意请求，替换或污染缓存中的合法内容，导致后续用户访问时被重定向至恶意资源或获取被篡改的数据。该漏洞源于缓存引擎对内容更新缺乏充分的访问控制与校验机制，影响使用思科缓存引擎的网络环境。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0998"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.483","remediation":"将 Cisco Cache Engine 软件升级至版本 3.2.1 或更高版本，该版本修复了缓存内容替换漏洞。若无法升级，可在网络边界配置 ACL，限制仅信任源访问 Cache Engine 的管理接口（TCP 80）和代理端口（TCP 3128/8080），并禁用不必要的远程管理功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0998","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0998.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0998","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0998.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87024/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0830.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0829","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0829.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0566","title":"IBM AIX syslog 日志填充拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 系统中的 syslog 组件存在日志写入权限缺陷，攻击者可从任意位置向 syslog 文件写入大量日志条目，导致磁盘空间被占满从而引发拒绝服务。同时，恶意日志会淹没正常审计记录，掩盖攻击者的操作痕迹，增加安全检测与溯源难度。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0566"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.053","remediation":"升级 IBM AIX 至 4.3.3 或更高版本，安装 APAR IX87386 补丁。同时配置 syslogd 限制远程写入（修改 /etc/syslog.conf 禁用非必要远程日志接收），在 /etc/hosts.allow 中限制 syslog 端口（UDP 514）的访问来源，并启用日志轮转（logrotate）防止单一日志文件过大导致磁盘写满。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0566","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0566","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0566.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7cvc-2mx4-55wc/GHSA-7cvc-2mx4-55wc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8aeb4aa9-e098-4c64-a9a7-a80928b5b3b8.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0829.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0828","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0828.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0565","title":"Sendmail 别名管道命令执行漏洞","description":"Sendmail 的别名（alias）功能允许将电子邮件内容通过管道（pipe）传递给指定程序执行，远程攻击者可利用此机制发送特制邮件触发目标系统执行任意命令，从而导致远程代码执行。该漏洞影响广泛使用的 Sendmail 邮件服务器软件，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级严重（CVSS 10.0），可导致服务器完全受控。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0565"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.933","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本，启用 smrsh（SendMail Restricted SHell）限制别名可调用的程序列表，仅允许白名单内的安全程序（如 mail、vacation）。同时在 /etc/mail/aliases 中移除或审查所有调用外部程序的管道别名，避免将未经消毒的输入传递给管道命令。如无法升级，可在 mc 配置中加入 FEATURE(smrsh) 并设置 smrsh 可执行路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0565","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0565.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0565.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0565","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0565.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0565.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0565.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0565.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86048/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0828.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0826","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0826.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0994","title":"Microsoft Windows NT SYSKEY 密码哈希加密密钥流重用漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中 SYSKEY 机制存在密钥流重用漏洞。SYSKEY 用于加密 SAM 数据库中的密码哈希，但由于其在加密过程中重复使用相同的密钥流，攻击者可通过分析多个加密后的密码哈希值，利用密钥流重用特性还原出明文密码。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，本地攻击者需具备系统访问权限，可通过暴力破解或差分分析手段获取用户凭据，导致系统账户安全受到威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0994"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.960","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本且无官方补丁。建议立即升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本操作系统，并启用 Kerberos 认证替代 NTLM；对于仍在使用 NT 的环境，应使用 SYSKEY 的增强模式（Syskey.exe /E）强制使用密码保护，并在注册表 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Lsa` 中设置 `NoLMHash=1` 禁用 LM Hash 存储以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ248183","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/873","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-056","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0994.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0994","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0994.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r7rj-gr4g-8x94/GHSA-r7rj-gr4g-8x94.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0826.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0825","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0825.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0562","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 空会话远程注册表访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 存在空会话（Null Session）远程访问注册表的权限漏洞。未经身份认证的攻击者可通过 SMB 协议建立空会话连接，远程匿名访问目标系统的注册表，获取系统配置、用户账户信息、网络共享设置等敏感数据。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 所有 SP 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。Microsoft 至今未完全移除该默认行为，需通过修改注册表或限制 IPC$ 访问进行缓解。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0562"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.693","remediation":"升级到 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a，并设置注册表项 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\LSA 下的 RestrictAnonymous 值为 2，禁止空会话枚举 SAM 账号和共享。同时禁用 NetBIOS over TCP/IP，在防火墙层面阻止 137-139、445 端口的外部入站连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A1023","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19372","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0562","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0562.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/Azure/Azure-Sentinel/blob/c359f282ec6bc3eb6912ee4649970789e923d257/Sample%20Data/Custom/beSECURE_ScanResults_CL.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6wh7-hrcm-fv9m/GHSA-6wh7-hrcm-fv9m.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_registry_access.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0825.toml"}]